                "text": "4 A student investigates the resistance of a wire.",
                "bbox": [
                    80,
                    73,
                    501,
                    89
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Plan an experiment which enables the student to investigate how the length of a wire affects the resistance of the wire.Resistance \\(R\\) is calculated from the equation: \\(R = \\frac{V}{I}\\)",
                "bbox": [
                    118,
                    140,
                    549,
                    170
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
